<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/435744-this-is-the-one-i-choose-for-our-read-the">This is the one I choose for our read. The Little Friend was so disappointing that I cannot find words to express my feelings. I also recently finished a novel about the violent South so I can&#39;t choose that again. Will All Over But.. be an opportunity to celebrate the South? That&#39;s what I am looking for.</a>
</div>
